    <div class="container grid-2">
      <div class="bp-text">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Loyalty Reimagined</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">The Con Leche<br/><em>Pase de Café</em></h2>
        <p class="section-body">Every drink you buy earns you a scan. Collect them, level up your tier, and unlock real rewards — vouchers, free drinks, merch, and more. Your unique QR code goes everywhere you go.</p>
        <div class="milestone-pills">
          <span class="pill pill-voucher">Drinks ending in 5 → Random voucher in store</span>
          <span class="pill pill-drink">Every 10th drink → Free drink (9 lives 🐾)</span>
          <span class="pill pill-merch">50 drinks → Free Cake & Cappuccino</span>
          <span class="pill pill-merch">100 drinks → Con Leche branded cap </span>
        </div>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Get Your QR Code</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bp-visual">
        <div class="bp-card-preview">
          <div class="bp-card-inner">
            <div class="bp-card-logo">
              <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Con Leche" />
            </div>
            <p class="bp-card-name">Your Name Here</p>
            <div class="bp-card-qr-placeholder">
              <div class="qr-grid"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bp-card-tier">
